          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Square Enix has brought over their previously Apple Arcade exclusive title ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Various Daylife",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " over to the Nintendo Switch with the team behind ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Octopath Traveller",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " taking the helm, as is evident by the art design. Set yourself up in your new life as you help a settlement explore an uncharted continent by taking on various jobs around town to build up your stats that allow you to then go out to the wilderness and perform some quest which is where the more traditional RPG game elements come into play. Take a chance on ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 2,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Various Daylife",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " with their experimental Cha-Cha-Cha combat system, allowing you to combo effects for big damage numbers.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
